lead_paragraph: "Elvis & Nixon," a comedy about the 1970 meeting between the king of rock 'n' roll and the president, will debut at the Tribeca Film Festival in New York.

headline.main: 'Elvis & Nixon' to Premiere at the Tribeca Film Festival
